snippet.title: Raining Blood Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Raining Blood is a bullet hell horde survival game with a huge arsenal of unique weapons and unlimited upgrades. Survive and explore to solve the puzzles of the demonic invasion.

Wishlist it now on Steam
